    "Theorem 5 (Primal-dual gap).",
    "Let Assumptions 3 and 4 hold.",
    "Then, it holds for Problem (P-CA) that-M + β + M λ best 1 ν ≤ D p (λ best) -P ⋆ ≤ ηS 2 2 + ϵ app + (M + β + M ∥λ ⋆ ν ∥ 1) ν (32)whereλ ⋆ ν:= argmin λ ≥ 0 D(λ) -M ν ∥λ∥ 1.Proof.",
